snippet.async_client:
import asyncio

from seed import AsyncSeedClientSideParams

client = AsyncSeedClientSideParams(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)


async def main() -> None:
    await client.service.list_resources(
        page=1,
        per_page=1,
        sort="created_at",
        order="desc",
        include_totals=True,
        fields="fields",
        search="search",
    )


asyncio.run(main())
